# Childmath Keepalive

[![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-blue)](LICENSE)
[![Chrome](https://img.shields.io/badge/Chrome-Extension-4285F4?logo=googlechrome&logoColor=white)](#)

![Header](assets/header.png)

One-line description.

> Minimal, clean, no UI changes to ChildsMath.

## Contents
- [Download](#download)
- [Install](#install)
- [Use](#use)
- [How to know it works](#how-to-know-it-works)
- [Troubleshooting](#troubleshooting)
- [License](#license)

## Download
- **GitHub ZIP:** Click **Code** → **Download ZIP**
- **Release ZIP (recommended):** Go to **Releases** and download `childsmath-keepalive.zip`

## Install
1. Unzip the download.
2. Open `chrome://extensions`
3. Enable **Developer mode**
4. Click **Load unpacked**
5. Select the folder that contains `manifest.json`

## Use
1. Log into ChildsMath.
2. Click the extension icon.
3. Toggle **On**.

![Popup](assets/popup.png)

## How to know it works
- Wait ~6–7 minutes.
- Open the popup:
  - **Last ping** updates
  - **Last result** shows `OK`
- Real test: leave ChildsMath idle for 20–30 minutes and confirm you are not logged out.

## Troubleshooting
- **Network error:** internet/blocked request.
- **Logged out detected:** ping URL may need to be changed.

